### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userRole": "USER",
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "test12!",
  "nickName": "user1"
}


### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "test12!"
}